info.pavie.opennetworkmap.model.draw.network.grid

Class Canvas

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.pavie.opennetworkmap.model.draw.network.grid.Canvas
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RepresentableNetwork

    public class Canvas
extends java.lang.Object
implements RepresentableNetwork
    A canvas is an editable table where you can insert Network vertices. It is a grid of different Layers, which allows to insert disconnected graphs. It allows to create a schematic representation of the network in a simple way.
